        <Summary>Minimalistic window manager</Summary>
        <Description>Ratpoison is a simple window manager that relies solely on keyboard input as opposed to keyboard and mouse input.</Description>
        <Archive sha1sum="e32430de49c4ab5d501653c03dd19dfb623cb08b" type="targz">http://download.savannah.nongnu.org/releases/ratpoison/ratpoison-1.4.5.tar.gz</Archive>
